Feature: Count star

  Background: a table with some data

    Given the table test
      | c       |
      | INTEGER |
      | 1       |
      | 2       |
      | 3       |

  Scenario: I count the number of rows in a table

    When I execute the query
    """
    SELECT COUNT(*) FROM test
    """

    Then I expect the result set
      | count(*) |
      | INTEGER  |
      | 3        |

